Package: polydice
Type: Package
Title: Simulate dice rolling in role playing games (RPGs)
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Alan Keegan
Maintainer: Alan Keegan <alan@statstutor.co.nz>
Description: Simulate dice rolls for role playing games (RPGs) such as Dungeons and Dragons (DnD). This package provides functions for the seven dice set - 4, 8, 10, 12, 20 sided dice and percentile rolls. They are wrapper functions for sample().
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/ajkeegan/polydice
BugReports: https://github.com/ajkeegan/polydice/issues
